UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.Mix.Description: Determines how much of the audio output is processed by the effect.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.AllowPortSelection: Determines if the Patchwork Tool can access any cable input or output ports on the device.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.EnabledOnPhase.Des: Determines the game phases during which the device will be enabled. Pre-game includes all phases prior to start of game (like the pre-game lobby or countdown to start of game.) This setting does not affect Edit Mode.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.Disable.Descriptio: Disables the device when an event occurs.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.Enable.Description: Enables the device when an event occurs.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.LegalInfo.Descript: Please note: Use of a Patchwork audio device is limited to the creation of new and original musical works.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.FilterType.Descrip: Selects which filter behavior will be applied, relative to the Cutoff value. Low-pass will attenuate frequencies above the cutoff, High-pass will attenuate frequencies below, Band-pass will attenuate frequencies on either side, and Notch will attenuate frequencies in the center.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.Resonance.Descript: Sets a range around the Cutoff value within which audio frequencies will be boosted.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.Cutoff.Description: Sets the audio frequency around which the selected Filter Type will be applied.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.AudioOut.Descripti: Sets the destination for this device's Audio Out cable.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.AudioIn.Descriptio: Sets the inputs for this device's Audio In port.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.CutoffIn.Descripti: Sets the inputs for this device's Cutoff knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.FilterTypeIn.Descr: Sets the inputs for this device's Filter Type carousel.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.MixIn.Description: Sets the inputs for this device's Mix knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.ResonanceIn.Descri: Sets the inputs for this device's Resonance knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.OnDisabled.Descrip: Triggers an event when the device is disabled.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricFilter_C.OnEnabled.Descript: Triggers an event when the device is enabled.
